  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-119fve5\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"d6XP7dwp\">喜欢把“<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=763164228&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E5%A4%9A%E5%85%83%E5%8C%96&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">多元化<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>”视为“先进”，这就是最大的误解。</p><p data-pid=\"EjOonCPs\">支持者自诩“先进文明”的“<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=763164228&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E4%BD%BF%E5%BE%92&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">使徒<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>”，要来“落后”地区传播“福音”；而反对者则心甘情愿地戴上“<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=763164228&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E8%80%81%E4%BF%9D&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">老保<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>”的帽子以示抗争。</p><p data-pid=\"T67V93lW\">这种局面不仅不利于真正的先进思想的传播，反而把那些该扫进历史垃圾堆的真正老保给抬了出来。</p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
  "excerpt": "喜欢把“多元化”视为“先进”，这就是最大的误解。\n\n支持者自诩“先进文明”的“使徒”，要来“落后”地区传播“福音”；而反对者则心甘情愿地戴上“老保”的帽子以示抗争。\n\n这种局面不仅不利于真正的先进思想的传播，反而把那些该扫进历史垃圾堆的真正老保给抬了出来。",
